>> ignoring loss resistance and reactance, is 3.lambda^2 / 8.pi", then why 
>> do
>> you say that adding a ferrite to a small loop antenna greatly increases
>> its
>> capture area?
>>
>> I agree with the first statement about capture area, but not the second.
